events.description:
🧲 Attraction and aversion
   for sense objects

👀 Are rooted in the senses;

🚫 Yield to neither;

🚧 Truly, they are obstacles on the path

🕉️ Krishna 🕉️

👁️ The senses are said to be great;

🧠 Higher than the senses is the mind;

💡 Higher than the mind is Pure Intellect;

✨ Truly higher than Pure Intellect is He

🕉️ Krishna 🕉️

🙏 I am the offering;
   I am the sacrifice;
   I am the offering to the ancestors;

🌿 I am the kindling herb;

🕉️ I am the mantra;

🛢️ I am also the ghee,

🔥 And the fire,

🕯️ And the act of offering itself

🕉️ Krishna 🕉️
